{"tid":788473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［估地方］六十歲市長大跳妖怪手錶舞","createTime":"2018-08-21T13:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T06:15:49.000Z","uid":118080,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b6cc9e641b4e34dc07b0e105a9ac06988535ed36","tid":788473,"uid":118080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">台北市長柯文哲</span></span>上YouTuber蔡阿嘎嘅節目，大玩過三關：跳妖怪手錶舞、舉藍綠旗考反應、注音考聯想力。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">邊到嘅市長會比柯P更親民，用咁多時間玩埋曬啲無聊遊戲？仲要跳哂成隻舞唔喘氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港嘅官員連show都唔撚做，分分鐘連YouTuber係乜都唔知。淨係睇呢幾分鐘，已經知佢有幾熟悉台北，唔係靠背稿，不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/211014_3c02a4930bfb65a279132afe2e643548.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F211014_3c02a4930bfb65a279132afe2e643548.png&h=3309c031&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/211025_1dc6f3cb324b236d67fd6719b5108f24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F211025_1dc6f3cb324b236d67fd6719b5108f24.png&h=c6062648&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/211043_97186ec77978c936b7d047d4cafd6ace.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F211043_97186ec77978c936b7d047d4cafd6ace.png&h=262f3728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傳送門</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ugEnXlgc5vk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FugEnXlgc5vk&d=S8QnQbGsTr4p9EbuerVbS7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=981c268a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ugEnXlgc5vk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">之前仲上過蔡阿嘎尬台語，俾人貼到成面標籤都冇發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/212437_3f64f999ee2aefb9d53ea7a501a3c81e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F212437_3f64f999ee2aefb9d53ea7a501a3c81e.png&h=508edd35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/212451_ad485f362d446bdf76c2087295e4340b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F212451_ad485f362d446bdf76c2087295e4340b.png&h=6c7e6ee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我愛柯P</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我愛柯P</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我愛柯P</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c94afc6527368605d4d1081153b608c9de4f5f","tid":788473,"uid":118080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ba7acff67378a72f28ab06dc9f11309c314fc35","tid":788473,"uid":118080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:52:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"453a85f16408afbcc256c61fb40f3b109dd51c0b","tid":788473,"uid":4826,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"點解香港個個咁撚食屎"},{"pid":"c61c75a1a41ef68ae64b8870e4